      "detail": "Revenue sharing ties data contributors' compensation to the infrastructure's commercial performance over the long commitment period through contractual formulae. Share calculations must continue to work fairly and accurately across model transitions, market changes, and competitive evolution over the period. The revenue-share mechanism is effectively a long-duration financial instrument that must remain meaningful across decades of commercial change. Its enforceability, fairness, and commercial relevance across the full lifecycle is itself a significant governance challenge requiring active management."
